{"tid":958572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5澳門狗美國過新生  340頭尚待領養","createTime":"2018-12-28T02:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T03:35:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c4abd64eaa31df2a1bfcee87809d996126a50b","tid":958572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20181228/s00046/6989c79f9cd5f2440799655efb6674cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20181228%2Fs00046%2F6989c79f9cd5f2440799655efb6674cc.jpg&h=0a09a97f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】澳門逸園狗場今年中關閉後，曾向澳門民政總署提交多份安置格力犬的計劃，惟逸園最終未能提供合適的場所妥善安置格力犬。逸園狗場原本共有500多隻格力犬，至昨日，共有161隻格力犬被領養，其中5隻格力犬日前已抵達美國展開新生活。現時狗場內尚餘340隻格力犬。<br />\n<br />\n美組織︰環境惡劣體重過輕<br />\n<br />\n澳門民政總署昨發稿稱，今年10月15日至12月24日期間，一共有151隻格力犬被領養，昨日再安排10隻格力犬予海外領養者領養。澳門逸園賽狗股份有限公司行政總裁李志文回應本報查詢時指出，一直全力配合民政總署及澳門愛護動物協會進行格力犬領養工作。<br />\n<br />\n澳門民署料罰逸園2500萬<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒霍士新聞（Fox News）報道，美國得州非牟利組織Greyhound Rescue Austin近日從澳門領養5隻格力犬，現時正在寄養家庭生活，等候公眾申請領養。該組織成員Sandi Reinlie指出，部分從狗場拯救出來的格力犬，因環境惡劣，均有體重過輕問題。她指這些格力犬除了脫離惡劣的生活環境，亦避免被賣至內地被吃掉。<br />\n<br />\n澳門民政總署與環境保護局於10月初到逸園安置格力犬的場地視察，惟場所的噪音防治措施仍未滿足技術意見要求，因此逸園未具條件領回狗場內的500多隻格力犬。由於逸園未能於民署定下的限期前領回格力犬，澳門傳媒本月中報道，民署已按《動物保護法》檢控逸園遺棄動物，建議每隻格力犬罰款5萬元澳門幣，作為照顧狗的費用，估計共罰款2500萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181228/s00002/1545934666602/5%E6%A0%BC%E5%8A%9B%E7%8A%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F-340%E9%A0%AD%E5%B0%9A%E5%BE%85%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181228%2Fs00002%2F1545934666602%2F5%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%258A%25AC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2594%259F-340%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%258A&d=71pwVW65x16IUdXCvZTcCE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=319b5782\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181228%2Fs00002%2F1545934666602%2F5%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%258A%25AC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2594%259F-340%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%258A&h=3bb7bd33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181228/s00002/1545934666602/5%E6%A0%BC%E5%8A%9B%E7%8A%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F-340%E9%A0%AD%E5%B0%9A%E5%BE%85%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%8A</a>"},{"pid":"1d89670583daa825b4d1340183dc7bff036d036c","tid":958572,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f03a088f7a6b807dc9e40efb7eb1f2f34e2958d3","tid":958572,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1d89670583daa825b4d1340183dc7bff036d036c","tid":958572,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"大陸狗就死番大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf71e7bc8410d060842f00236253a4db8ca9cea","tid":958572,"uid":140041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03a088f7a6b807dc9e40efb7eb1f2f34e2958d3","tid":958572,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1d89670583daa825b4d1340183dc7bff036d036c","tid":958572,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"大陸狗就死番大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"大陸狗只會比人殺黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e4f1762e9ffe49d3ade023ed5f764d71a0730d","tid":958572,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"